Kenya has become a sanctuary
of sorts

19:09.217 --> 19:13.186
for a number of diverse ethnic, political, and social groups.

19:13.221 --> 19:14.843
♪

19:14.877 --> 19:17.604
One such group with
a steadily growing nucleus

19:17.639 --> 19:19.434
is the LGBT
community,

19:19.468 --> 19:22.885
not too long ago, a nearly
unthinkable development.

19:22.920 --> 19:25.923
