20:28.088 --> 20:29.538
- Yeah.
- So like--

20:29.573 --> 20:30.781
[voices overlapping]

20:30.815 --> 20:32.438
- They're just
one penis short.

20:32.472 --> 20:34.025
- I'm the one they're missing.
- Yeah, you know.

20:34.060 --> 20:37.512
Like, they need me to
help them out with a dick,

20:37.546 --> 20:38.789
but if you--

20:38.823 --> 20:41.032
- Yeah, there's
an abundance.

20:41.067 --> 20:43.690
- And the violence,
like, again is like

20:43.725 --> 20:46.624
lesbians always comes in
the part where, like,

20:46.659 --> 20:48.385
men realize, oh, they're
not attracted to me.

20:48.419 --> 20:51.526
- I've always had this theory
that a lot of the issues

20:51.560 --> 20:53.597
and discrimination
