22:01.906 --> 22:03.114
- Yes.
- Yeah.

22:03.149 --> 22:04.530
- Why scared?

22:04.564 --> 22:05.876
- Backlash, obviously.
- Yeah.

22:05.910 --> 22:07.705
- What'll happen,
there'll be people who--

22:07.740 --> 22:09.604
there'll be people
who will be attacked.

22:09.638 --> 22:11.537
- Yeah.
- I mean,

22:11.571 --> 22:15.955
we're moving to an extreme end
