a staple green across
Swahili speaking Africa

26:51.333 --> 26:53.853
from Tanzania
to Mozambique.

26:53.888 --> 26:56.856
Beans with onions
and coconut milk,

26:56.891 --> 27:00.929
chicken biryani with masala,
