- ♪ Everyone go amok and groovy ♪

33:56.103 --> 33:58.174
- ♪ Move it, move it,
move it, move it ♪

33:58.208 --> 33:59.727
- ♪ Everyone go amok and groovy ♪

33:59.761 --> 34:01.384
- ♪ Move it, move it,
move it, yeah ♪

34:01.418 --> 34:03.213
- ♪ Everyone go amok and groovy ♪

34:03.248 --> 34:05.526
- ♪ Move it, move it,
move it, move it ♪

